\c 1
\s Ukufa kukaAhaziya
\p
\v 1 UMowabi wasevukela\x + 2 Sam. 8.2.\x* uIsrayeli emva kokufa kukaAhabi\x + 3.5.\x*.
\v 2 UAhaziya wasesiwa eminxibeni yewindi ekamelweni lakhe eliphezulu eliseSamariya, wagula\x + Hlu. 3.20.\x*. Wathuma izithunywa, wathi kuzo: Hambani li\add ye\add*buza kuBhali-Zebhubi\x + 1.3,6,16. Mat. 10.25. 12.24,27. Mark. 3.22. Luka 11.15,18,19.\x* unkulunkulu weEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x* ukuthi ngizasila yini emkhuhlaneni lo\x + 8.8.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuElija umTishibi\x + 1 Kho. 21.17.\x*: Sukuma, wenyuke ukuhlangabeza izithunywa zenkosi yeSamariya, uthi kizo: Kungenxa yokuthi kakulaNkulunkulu yini koIsrayeli ukuthi lihambe li\add ye\add*buza kuBhali-Zebhubi\x + 1.3,6,16. Mat. 10.25. 12.24,27. Mark. 3.22. Luka 11.15,18,19.\x* unkulunkulu weEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*?
\v 4 Ngakho-ke itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Umbheda owenyukele kuwo kawuyikwehla kuwo, ngoba uzakufa lokufa. UElija wasehamba.
\p
\v 5 Lapho izithunywa sezibuyele kuyo, wathi kuzo: Kungani selibuyile?
\v 6 Zasezisithi kuyo: Umuntu wenyukile ukusihlangabeza, wathi kithi: Hambani libuyele enkosini elithumileyo, lithi kuyo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Kungenxa yokuthi kakulaNkulunkulu koIsrayeli yini ukuthi uthumele ukubuza kuBhali-Zebhubi\x + 1.3,6,16. Mat. 10.25. 12.24,27. Mark. 3.22. Luka 11.15,18,19.\x* unkulunkulu weEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*? Ngakho umbheda owenyukele kuwo kawuyikwehla kuwo, ngoba sibili uzakufa.
\v 7 Yasisithi kuzo: Besinjani isimo salowomuntu owenyukele ukulihlangabeza, wakhuluma kini lamazwi?
\v 8 Basebesithi kuyo: Ubeyindoda eloboya, ebophe ngozwezwe lwesikhumba ekhalweni lwayo\x + Gen. 37.19. Gen. 25.25. 27.11. Isa. 20.2. Zek. 13.4. Mat. 3.4. Mark. 1.6.\x*. Yasisithi: NguElija umTishibi\x + 1 Kho. 21.17.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Inkosi yasithuma kuye induna yabangamatshumi amahlanu labangamatshumi amahlanu bayo. Yasisenyukela kuye; khangela-ke, wayehlezi engqongeni yentaba; yathi kuye: Muntu kaNkulunkulu, inkosi ithe: Yehla\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x*.
\v 10 UElija wasephendula wathi enduneni yabangamatshumi amahlanu: Uba-ke ngingumuntu kaNkulunkulu, kakwehle umlilo ovela emazulwini uqothule wena labangamatshumi amahlanu bakho. Wasusehla umlilo uvela emazulwini, wayiqothula yona labangamatshumi amahlanu bayo\x + Luka 9.54.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Yasibuya ithuma kuye enye induna yabangamatshumi amahlanu labangamatshumi amahlanu bayo. Yasiphendula yathi kuye: Muntu kaNkulunkulu, itsho njalo inkosi: Yehla masinyane.
\v 12 UElija wasephendula wathi kubo: Uba ngingumuntu kaNkulunkulu, kakwehle umlilo ovela emazulwini uqothule wena labangamatshumi amahlanu bakho. Wasusehla umlilo kaNkulunkulu uvela emazulwini, wayiqothula yona labangamatshumi amahlanu bayo\x + Jobe 1.16.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Yasithuma futhi induna yabangamatshumi amahlanu besithathu labangamatshumi amahlanu bayo. Leyonduna yesithathu yabangamatshumi amahlanu yasisenyuka yeza yawa ngamadolo ayo phambi kukaElija, yamncenga yathi kuye: Muntu kaNkulunkulu, ake ibe ligugu impilo yami lempilo yalezi inceku zakho ezingamatshumi amahlanu emehlweni akho\x + 1.14. 1 Sam. 26.21. Hlab. 72.14. 1 Sam. 18.30.\x*.
\v 14 Khangela, wehla umlilo uvela emazulwini, waqothula induna ezimbili zabangamatshumi amahlanu zokuqala labangamatshumi amahlanu azo; ngakho-ke kayibe ligugu impilo yami emehlweni akho.
\v 15 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuElija: Yehla laye, ungamesabi. Wasesukuma, wehla laye waya enkosini;
\v 16 wathi kuyo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngenxa yokuthi uthume izithunywa ukuyabuza kuBhali-Zebhubi\x + 1.3,6,16. Mat. 10.25. 12.24,27. Mark. 3.22. Luka 11.15,18,19.\x*, unkulunkulu weEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*, kungenxa yokuthi kakulaNkulunkulu koIsrayeli yini, ukubuza ilizwi lakhe? Ngakho-ke umbheda owenyukele kuwo kawuyikwehla kuwo, ngoba uzakufa lokufa.
\p
\v 17 Wasesifa njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uElija ayelikhulumile. UJehoramu wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe, ngomnyaka wesibili kaJoramu indodana kaJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda, ngoba wayengelandodana.
\p
\v 18 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAhaziya, azenzayo, kazibhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?